WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.320 --> 02:49.980
[Episode 27]

02:50.000 --> 02:51.820
You were involved in

02:51.840 --> 02:54.120
all of Bai Shuo's pain.

02:54.150 --> 02:55.360
I'm not Bai Xi.

02:55.360 --> 02:56.590
I'm not!

02:56.610 --> 02:58.130
Since you're in so much pain,

02:58.150 --> 03:00.210
why don't you let me finish you off?

03:00.710 --> 03:01.650
Anyway,

03:01.670 --> 03:03.270
the person I really wanted to find

03:03.300 --> 03:04.850
was never you.

03:11.320 --> 03:13.060
Master, please spare Fu Ling.

03:14.990 --> 03:16.620
You are not surprised at all?

03:16.650 --> 03:17.760
It seems

03:18.079 --> 03:19.960
you already knew her identity.

03:19.980 --> 03:21.700
No matter if she's Fu Ling or Bai Xi,

03:21.730 --> 03:23.520
she won’t be a threat to the you.

03:23.540 --> 03:24.870
As long as you let her go,

03:24.900 --> 03:25.810
I, Chong Zhao,

03:25.829 --> 03:27.079
will serve you tirelessly.

03:27.390 --> 03:28.440
She is

03:28.460 --> 03:30.020
this important to you?

03:33.660 --> 03:34.610
Sure.

03:35.290 --> 03:36.360
I can

03:36.380 --> 03:37.550
spare her life.

03:37.570 --> 03:38.960
But from now on,

03:38.980 --> 03:39.980
she is not allowed

03:40.010 --> 03:41.590
to leave her room again.

03:41.620 --> 03:42.280
Otherwise...

03:42.280 --> 03:43.750
I will discipline her.

03:44.329 --> 03:45.520
You may leave.

03:58.570 --> 03:59.520
Fan Yue,

03:59.880 --> 04:02.270
I can easily test to see if you were

04:02.680 --> 04:05.060
one of the three children or not.

04:13.550 --> 04:14.710
Leave.

04:14.940 --> 04:15.820
I won't.

04:16.720 --> 04:17.810
I want to watch over you.

04:17.839 --> 04:18.839
Do you want to watch over me

04:18.870 --> 04:20.360
or Bai Xi?

04:29.520 --> 04:31.470
No matter if you're Fu Ling or Bai Xi,

04:32.550 --> 04:33.800
I will watch over you.

04:34.159 --> 04:35.240
No.

04:36.200 --> 04:37.960
I can't be Bai Xi.

04:38.100 --> 04:40.360
This is all Zhen Yu's conspiracy.

04:38.500 --> 04:43.640
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

04:40.690 --> 04:41.990
I am Fu Ling.

04:42.630 --> 04:44.390
I am a demon.

04:45.380 --> 04:48.230
I'm just a failure abandoned by my parents.

04:46.920 --> 04:52.250
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

04:49.090 --> 04:51.500
I'm definitely not Bai Xi.

04:54.909 --> 05:02.340
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

05:03.260 --> 05:08.310
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

05:03.380 --> 05:04.580
What are you doing?

05:04.710 --> 05:07.200
Zhen Yu gave me all my demonic power.

05:07.680 --> 05:08.920
I don't want his stuff.

05:08.920 --> 05:10.350
I'll give it back to him.

05:10.680 --> 05:12.360
You don't owe Zhen Yu anything.

05:12.390 --> 05:13.480
He owes you.

05:18.060 --> 05:19.140
Fu Ling.

05:19.980 --> 05:22.330
I've passed the secret of Cold Spring Palace to Lanling.

05:22.440 --> 05:24.820
The Eternals will soon come to attack Cold Spring Palace.

05:24.850 --> 05:25.940
By then,

05:26.630 --> 05:28.230
I'll take you to leave this place.

05:28.680 --> 05:32.020
♫Across thousands of miles♫

05:29.910 --> 05:31.460
Leave here?

05:32.230 --> 05:33.390
And go where?

05:33.640 --> 05:35.280
To Lanling with you?

05:36.070 --> 05:38.750
I'm a demoness who has done all the bad things.

05:36.800 --> 05:41.590
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

05:38.870 --> 05:40.710
If I go back with you to the Eternals,

05:41.030 --> 05:43.270
they will kill me immediately.

05:43.290 --> 05:45.050
I won't let them kill you.

05:44.330 --> 05:51.390
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

05:45.830 --> 05:47.040
You're in this state now

05:47.040 --> 05:48.390
because Zhen Yu forced you to.

05:48.620 --> 05:49.690
Don’t worry.

05:51.020 --> 05:52.780
I will explain everything to the Eternals.

05:52.510 --> 05:57.340
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

05:52.800 --> 05:54.200
Why don’t you understand?

05:55.120 --> 05:56.540
I'm not Bai Xi.

05:56.570 --> 05:58.690
Bai Xi died ten years ago.

05:58.710 --> 06:00.000
I'm just Fu Ling.

06:00.030 --> 06:01.300
Also,

06:00.420 --> 06:05.940
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

06:01.320 --> 06:02.570
my life and death

06:02.600 --> 06:03.980
has nothing to do with you.

06:07.060 --> 06:08.250
Leave.

06:08.650 --> 06:14.190
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

06:08.840 --> 06:10.040
I'm tired.

06:16.010 --> 06:17.530
I'll be outside.

06:16.950 --> 06:24.070
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

06:24.420 --> 06:29.610
♫I'm your wanderer♫

06:26.280 --> 06:29.440
I'm willing to exchange my life

06:30.020 --> 06:32.000
for the safety...

06:32.710 --> 06:34.600
No!

06:34.620 --> 06:36.210
Of a city!

06:38.190 --> 06:40.090
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

06:38.530 --> 06:40.640
Father!

06:40.190 --> 06:42.130
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

06:42.360 --> 06:44.030
♫My love brought tears♫

06:44.240 --> 06:46.210
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

06:46.480 --> 06:48.230
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

06:48.490 --> 06:49.700
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

06:50.050 --> 06:51.659
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

06:52.110 --> 06:53.810
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

06:54.480 --> 06:55.970
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

06:56.340 --> 06:57.940
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

06:56.659 --> 06:58.030
I'm Chenxi.

06:58.060 --> 06:59.570
You're Xingyue,

06:58.260 --> 07:00.230
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

06:59.590 --> 07:01.110
bright and starry,

07:00.600 --> 07:02.380
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

07:01.140 --> 07:02.840
breaking through the clouds.

07:02.700 --> 07:04.400
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

07:02.930 --> 07:04.320
Our dearest Shuo

07:04.350 --> 07:06.450
will be like the stars and moon in the sky,

07:04.630 --> 07:06.520
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

07:06.580 --> 07:08.020
The darker the night is,

07:06.920 --> 07:08.560
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

07:08.050 --> 07:09.250
the brighter you'll shine.

07:08.640 --> 07:11.040
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

07:09.270 --> 07:10.600
Once you decide,

07:10.630 --> 07:11.960
you can go down.

07:12.210 --> 07:13.930
I'll always be behind you.

07:59.710 --> 08:01.760
Even if you are not Bai Xi,

08:02.720 --> 08:04.040
I will protect you.

08:13.120 --> 08:13.930
Master.

08:16.890 --> 08:18.150
Let's talk outside.

08:20.320 --> 08:21.360
You mean the demon with

08:21.360 --> 08:23.290
the black snake tattoo on his arm is Zhen Yu?

08:23.510 --> 08:24.580
That's right.

08:24.610 --> 08:26.930
I asked Nuo to draw the black snake mark

08:26.950 --> 08:28.680
and dispatched all spies in Bright Moon Palace.

08:28.710 --> 08:29.660
They found out

08:29.680 --> 08:31.290
Zhen Yu was not born into the Dragon Clan

08:31.310 --> 08:33.299
but was a snake that transformed into a dragon.

08:33.330 --> 08:34.450
The black snake tattoo

08:34.470 --> 08:35.950
was done by Zhen Yu.

08:35.970 --> 08:37.490
Ten years ago,

08:37.520 --> 08:39.789
only a few demons could make the Tiger King obey them.

08:39.940 --> 08:41.570
Zhen Yu was one of them.

08:42.049 --> 08:44.450
But why is he looking for the boy with purple eyes?

08:47.280 --> 08:48.510
Qi Feng?

08:49.850 --> 08:50.650
Qi Feng!

08:51.930 --> 08:53.930
Qi Feng didn't go back to serve Zhen Yu

08:53.950 --> 08:55.610
but to avenge the Bai Ze Clan.

08:55.640 --> 08:57.210
He didn’t kill Nuo

08:57.230 --> 08:58.790
because he has the Contemplation of kindness.

09:00.610 --> 09:01.730
What's wrong?

09:02.120 --> 09:03.330
What else did you find out?

09:06.340 --> 09:08.160
I just received news from the Cold Spring Palace.

09:08.190 --> 09:10.310
Chen Ye rebelled and tried to assassinate Zhen Yu.

09:10.340 --> 09:13.230
Zhen Yu will publicly execute Chen Ye tonight.

09:13.260 --> 09:14.170
Tian Huo,

09:14.660 --> 09:16.070
guard Bai Shuo.

09:16.100 --> 09:17.410
Don't let her be disturbed.

09:17.430 --> 09:18.840
You’re going to Cold Spring Palace?

09:18.870 --> 09:19.900
I must personally avenge

09:19.920 --> 09:21.130
the Bai Ze Clan.

09:21.160 --> 09:23.190
But Zhen Yu suddenly released this kind of news.

09:23.210 --> 09:24.300
I'm afraid he has found out

09:24.330 --> 09:25.560
your relationship with Chen Ye

09:25.580 --> 09:27.770
and is deliberately setting you up.

09:28.440 --> 09:30.360
Do you think I’m afraid of Zhen Yu?

09:30.390 --> 09:31.630
That's not what I meant.

09:31.650 --> 09:33.500
But Zhen Yu is sinister and cunning.

09:33.530 --> 09:35.200
I’d better go with you.

09:35.220 --> 09:37.190
Bai Shuo is at the critical moment.

09:37.240 --> 09:38.600
She can't be disturbed.

09:38.620 --> 09:39.860
Guarding Bai Shuo

09:39.890 --> 09:41.420
is your most important task now.

09:41.480 --> 09:43.500
But protecting you, Master, is my mission.

09:43.520 --> 09:44.640
This is an order.

09:44.970 --> 09:46.640
If you still regard me as your master

09:46.670 --> 09:48.470
and you still see yourself as the guardian of Bright Moon Palace,

09:48.500 --> 09:49.860
obey my order.

10:06.020 --> 10:07.420
Let me ask you.

10:08.400 --> 10:09.330
Chen Ye

10:09.350 --> 10:10.540
acted unfavorably

10:10.570 --> 10:11.860
and failed his mission.

10:11.890 --> 10:12.850
What should we do?

10:12.870 --> 10:14.070
Kill him!

10:15.760 --> 10:17.640
Let me continue to ask.

10:17.660 --> 10:18.780
Chen Ye

10:18.810 --> 10:20.220
colluded with enemies

10:20.240 --> 10:21.730
and plotted a rebellion.

10:21.760 --> 10:22.760
What should we do?

10:22.790 --> 10:24.250
Kill him!

10:25.660 --> 10:27.720
Let me ask you one last time.

10:28.090 --> 10:30.720
Not only did Chen Ye disobey me,

10:30.740 --> 10:32.230
but also assassinated me.

10:32.260 --> 10:33.740
What should we do?

10:33.760 --> 10:35.950
Kill! Kill! Kill!

10:43.000 --> 10:44.880
My today

10:45.470 --> 10:47.550
will be your tomorrow.

10:48.260 --> 10:49.430
Zhen Yu,

10:49.650 --> 10:52.030
those who do evil will be punished by death.

10:52.730 --> 10:54.320
All the eternals and demons

10:54.350 --> 10:56.090
who want to kill you will flood over

10:56.110 --> 10:57.500
and flatten Cold Spring Palace.

10:57.530 --> 10:59.050
Flatten Cold Spring Palace?

11:00.500 --> 11:01.900
Do you know

11:01.930 --> 11:03.810
what I'm plotting?

11:05.140 --> 11:06.540
Once my plan

11:06.570 --> 11:07.720
succeeds,

11:09.130 --> 11:10.440
only the Cold Spring Palace

11:10.460 --> 11:12.240
will remain in this world.

11:12.260 --> 11:13.440
Zhen Yu!

11:13.590 --> 11:15.390
How arrogant!

11:17.420 --> 11:18.420
Today,

11:18.450 --> 11:20.120
I will make this Cold Spring Palace

11:20.140 --> 11:21.420
no longer exist.

11:30.490 --> 11:31.180
Qi Feng.

11:31.210 --> 11:32.280
Who told you to come?

11:32.300 --> 11:33.230
Go!

11:33.260 --> 11:34.980
I set up a trap with Chen Ye.

11:35.000 --> 11:36.090
You came as expected.

11:36.120 --> 11:37.930
If I guessed correctly,

11:37.950 --> 11:39.420
you’re also from the Bai Ze Clan, right?

11:39.770 --> 11:40.660
The boy

11:40.860 --> 11:43.580
with purple eyes I wanted to find before

11:43.610 --> 11:45.800
was you, right?

11:46.280 --> 11:47.330
Back then, Chen Ye

11:47.350 --> 11:49.310
exchanged identities to protect you.

11:49.470 --> 11:50.950
If I were you,

11:50.970 --> 11:52.300
I would come to save him too.

11:52.330 --> 11:53.700
Fan Yue,

11:53.730 --> 11:55.710
I don't need your pity

11:55.740 --> 11:57.380
nor need you to save me.

11:57.400 --> 11:58.370
Go!

11:58.400 --> 11:59.240
Chen Ye,

11:59.260 --> 12:01.980
you treat him sincerely.

12:02.540 --> 12:03.690
It’s not your place

12:03.710 --> 12:05.420
to teach my men a lesson.

12:06.140 --> 12:07.880
Zhen Yu has a mysterious power

12:07.960 --> 12:09.320
that's neither eternal nor demonic.

12:09.790 --> 12:11.310
It's hard to fight him.

12:11.360 --> 12:12.400
I'll take you away.

12:13.170 --> 12:14.830
I'm dying.

12:15.020 --> 12:17.500
Zhen Yu never thought of letting me leave alive.

12:17.960 --> 12:19.840
I’ll leave Bai Ze’s revenge to you.

12:20.300 --> 12:21.580
Go!

12:21.600 --> 12:22.430
Go!

12:22.460 --> 12:24.150
Neither of you can leave.

12:33.670 --> 12:34.960
All these years,

12:35.010 --> 12:37.180
I've been killing demons everywhere.

12:37.200 --> 12:38.330
Do you really think

12:38.350 --> 12:40.610
I did it to repair the dragon tail?

12:41.610 --> 12:43.770
That's just a cover-up.

12:43.800 --> 12:45.160
I fed

12:45.180 --> 12:46.780
all the demon cores

12:46.810 --> 12:48.170
to this ancient mirror.

12:48.520 --> 12:50.330
As long as enough demonic power is absorbed,

12:50.360 --> 12:52.670
the ancient mirror can be completely restored.

12:52.690 --> 12:54.410
The person I want to meet

12:54.440 --> 12:56.350
will be back soon.

13:05.100 --> 13:06.010
Come with me.

13:08.000 --> 13:09.290
Fan Yue is attacking the Cold Spring Palace.

13:09.320 --> 13:10.720
Zhen Yu is busy with Fan Yue.

13:10.740 --> 13:12.530
Now is our best chance to leave Cold Spring Palace.

13:12.560 --> 13:14.130
I said I'm not going anywhere.

13:14.150 --> 13:15.270
You can leave by yourself.

13:19.380 --> 13:20.700
I must

13:21.150 --> 13:23.100
bring you out of this hell.

13:32.500 --> 13:33.700
This is

13:33.730 --> 13:35.980
an ancient Divine Mirror from 60,000 years ago.

13:36.000 --> 13:37.900
Ordinary power can't counter it.

13:37.930 --> 13:39.840
Fan Yue, your demonic power

13:39.860 --> 13:41.580
is much more useful

13:41.610 --> 13:42.980
than ordinary demon cores.

13:50.390 --> 13:53.180
It can heal the cracks of the Divine Mirror.

13:53.200 --> 13:54.950
As expected of a Demon Lord's Divine Mantle.

13:54.980 --> 13:56.830
If I'm not mistaken,

13:56.860 --> 13:59.130
you are a snake of the Divine Region from 60,000 years ago.

13:59.220 --> 14:01.110
That's why you could cultivate into a dragon.

14:01.650 --> 14:03.530
You could cure Chen Ye's legs

14:03.560 --> 14:04.510
because you have a bit

14:04.510 --> 14:05.980
of the Hidden Race's power.

14:06.010 --> 14:07.410
Good guess.

14:07.430 --> 14:08.610
Unfortunately,

14:08.940 --> 14:10.820
you have no chance

14:10.840 --> 14:12.510
to compete with me anymore.

14:18.710 --> 14:19.760
Qi Feng!

14:25.260 --> 14:27.220
All my life, I've always

14:27.250 --> 14:29.710
forced my way out of dead ends.

14:29.940 --> 14:31.330
If I have no chance,

14:31.360 --> 14:32.790
then I'll create a chance.

14:33.350 --> 14:34.470
Zhen Yu,

14:34.680 --> 14:36.450
I won’t let you

14:36.620 --> 14:38.720
do any of the things that you want to do.

14:41.590 --> 14:43.490
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

14:43.790 --> 14:45.790
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

14:45.850 --> 14:47.330
♫My love brought tears♫

14:47.780 --> 14:49.610
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

14:50.030 --> 14:51.690
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

14:52.070 --> 14:53.100
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

14:53.700 --> 14:55.160
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

14:55.690 --> 14:57.270
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

14:58.030 --> 14:59.450
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

14:59.860 --> 15:01.510
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

15:01.780 --> 15:03.660
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

15:04.200 --> 15:05.780
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

15:06.080 --> 15:07.890
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

15:08.160 --> 15:10.070
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

15:10.460 --> 15:11.820
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

15:12.160 --> 15:14.620
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

15:17.910 --> 15:18.790
Qi Feng.

15:25.720 --> 15:26.850
Fan Yue.

15:45.500 --> 15:46.780
I forgive you this time.

15:46.800 --> 15:47.960
Don't do it again.

15:53.500 --> 15:56.890
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

15:57.920 --> 16:00.120
♫The last moonlight♫

16:01.570 --> 16:04.750
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

16:06.100 --> 16:08.730
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

16:09.420 --> 16:13.430
♫In this life, at this time♫

16:13.770 --> 16:17.110
♫I dare not look back♫

16:18.020 --> 16:21.120
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

16:22.390 --> 16:25.470
♫On your path?♫

16:26.300 --> 16:29.230
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

16:29.870 --> 16:33.010
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

16:33.990 --> 16:35.850
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

16:36.500 --> 16:38.330
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

16:38.850 --> 16:41.570
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

16:42.650 --> 16:45.700
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

16:45.870 --> 16:49.130
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

16:49.820 --> 16:52.140
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

16:52.560 --> 16:54.200
♫Time after time♫

16:54.780 --> 16:56.160
♫Again♫

16:58.740 --> 17:02.420
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

17:02.700 --> 17:05.670
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

17:03.590 --> 17:06.890
[Qi Feng]

17:06.430 --> 17:08.290
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

17:08.910 --> 17:11.010
[Qi Feng]

17:08.940 --> 17:10.450
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

17:10.680 --> 17:14.280
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

17:14.740 --> 17:18.450
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

17:18.680 --> 17:21.839
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

17:22.349 --> 17:24.450
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

17:23.099 --> 17:25.579
[Qi Feng]

17:24.819 --> 17:26.640
♫Time after time♫

17:27.220 --> 17:28.600
♫Again♫

17:41.810 --> 17:42.730
My Lord.

17:57.410 --> 17:58.350
Zhen Yu!

18:01.300 --> 18:02.690
A Demon Lord's Divine Mantle

18:02.720 --> 18:04.110
is nothing.

18:11.860 --> 18:12.820
Shuo.

18:18.180 --> 18:19.140
Shuo.

18:21.200 --> 18:23.200
I told you before in Ning'an City

18:23.220 --> 18:24.790
that I'll definitely kill you

18:24.950 --> 18:26.400
and avenge my father!

18:44.040 --> 18:45.040
Shuo.

18:45.810 --> 18:46.770
You overestimate yourself.

18:47.430 --> 18:48.630
In my eyes,

18:48.760 --> 18:50.880
you're just an ant.

18:50.900 --> 18:53.040
Even if I, Bai Shuo, am just an ant,

18:54.210 --> 18:55.860
dying by your hand

18:56.190 --> 18:57.700
is not my destiny.

19:04.030 --> 19:07.570
♫I've climbed 3,000 steps with a sincere heart♫

19:08.010 --> 19:10.670
♫I've prayed to the Buddha, burning incense, keeping to oneself♫

19:11.280 --> 19:14.050
♫Don't ask, don't separate, don't describe the universe anymore♫

19:14.670 --> 19:17.300
♫I only deserve to read poetry intoxicatingly♫

19:17.940 --> 19:20.940
♫I am an average person who fell into the mundane world♫

19:21.590 --> 19:24.560
♫Holding a lonely lamp to light up nirvana♫

19:25.210 --> 19:31.400
♫Don't approach, don't recognize, don't forget I'm not drifting♫

19:28.170 --> 19:29.610
Hurry and go, Shuo!

19:36.380 --> 19:37.550
If you fight with a strong opponent

19:37.580 --> 19:38.820
and your power is weaker than him,

19:38.840 --> 19:39.910
you can use the fastest speed

19:39.940 --> 19:41.770
and give a fatal surprise attack

19:41.880 --> 19:43.670
by seizing his only opening.

19:43.870 --> 19:45.570
Then, you can survive a desperate situation

19:45.810 --> 19:47.110
and turn defeat into victory.

19:47.460 --> 19:49.160
May we live and die together,

19:49.870 --> 19:51.590
and share life and death as one.

20:01.360 --> 20:03.160
But what if my opponent is Zhen Yu?

20:03.180 --> 20:04.380
He is the same.

20:04.410 --> 20:06.060
But this is just a move.

20:06.080 --> 20:07.430
He has great demonic power.

20:07.460 --> 20:09.110
Even if I find his opening,

20:09.380 --> 20:10.900
I can't take his life.

20:10.930 --> 20:12.140
But don't forget

20:12.390 --> 20:14.090
you still have the power of the Contemplation Stone.

20:14.230 --> 20:15.350
When you gather all your power

20:15.350 --> 20:16.700
to this move,

20:16.790 --> 20:18.080
not to mention Zhen Yu,

20:18.100 --> 20:19.140
you'll

20:19.170 --> 20:20.880
have a 70% chance

20:21.100 --> 20:22.380
to behead even me.

20:23.060 --> 20:24.450
It's not that easy

20:24.480 --> 20:26.060
for a human to defeat a demon.

20:26.190 --> 20:28.120
But remember your feelings and moves just now

20:28.140 --> 20:30.080
and get the knack of it.

20:30.570 --> 20:32.150
As long as you practice hard,

20:32.530 --> 20:34.170
and with the power of the Contemplation Stone,

20:34.200 --> 20:35.090
one day,

20:35.110 --> 20:36.700
even if you are to fight against the Demon King,

20:36.730 --> 20:37.970
you'll still have a chance to win.

20:49.460 --> 20:53.280
♫I've climbed 3,000 steps with a sincere heart♫

20:53.440 --> 20:56.230
♫I've prayed to the Buddha, burning incense, keeping to oneself♫

20:56.940 --> 20:59.720
♫Don't ask, don't separate, don't describe the universe anymore♫

21:00.620 --> 21:02.630
♫I only deserve to read poetry intoxicatingly♫

21:03.390 --> 21:06.440
♫I am an average person who fell into the mundane world♫

21:07.150 --> 21:10.220
♫Holding a lonely lamp to light up nirvana♫

21:10.890 --> 21:15.850
♫Don't approach, don't recognize, don't forget I'm not drifting♫

21:16.020 --> 21:17.040
Shuo.

21:16.510 --> 21:20.060
♫I've climbed 3,000 steps with a sincere heart♫

21:21.150 --> 21:23.180
♫I've prayed to the Buddha, burning incense, keeping to oneself♫

21:23.790 --> 21:26.930
♫Don't ask, don't separate, don't describe the universe anymore♫

21:27.420 --> 21:29.740
♫I only deserve to read poetry intoxicatingly♫

21:30.320 --> 21:33.740
♫I am an average person who fell into the mundane world♫

21:34.180 --> 21:37.130
♫Holding a lonely lamp to light up nirvana♫

21:37.950 --> 21:43.780
♫Don't approach, don't recognize, don't forget I'm not drifting♫

21:38.120 --> 21:39.280
Fan Yue.

21:40.010 --> 21:41.400
I'll take you home.

21:42.870 --> 21:44.210
Okay.

21:48.120 --> 21:48.950
Shuo.

22:02.660 --> 22:03.510
Shuo.

22:50.070 --> 22:51.240
It's beautiful!

22:51.480 --> 22:52.530
Look!

22:57.940 --> 23:01.220
♫Across thousands of miles♫

23:06.080 --> 23:10.620
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

23:07.900 --> 23:08.540
Master?

23:08.570 --> 23:09.400
Master?

23:09.420 --> 23:10.450
Master!

23:33.600 --> 23:34.630
Where is this?

23:48.210 --> 23:49.860
Why does it look familiar?

23:54.880 --> 23:55.960
Xi?

23:59.350 --> 23:59.980
Xi.

24:00.000 --> 24:01.510
Why didn't you go home yet?

24:01.540 --> 24:02.650
Let me send you home.

24:02.670 --> 24:04.310
Otherwise, Uncle Bai will be worried.

24:05.910 --> 24:06.840
Stop kneading.

24:06.860 --> 24:08.380
Your hands are red from the cold.

24:11.570 --> 24:13.730
Today is mother's death anniversary.

24:14.060 --> 24:16.330
Father has locked himself in his room.

24:16.350 --> 24:18.460
I want to make steamed buns with Mother's recipe

24:18.480 --> 24:20.420
for Father and Shuo,

24:20.450 --> 24:22.220
so they can be happier.

24:22.640 --> 24:23.400
Xi.

24:23.430 --> 24:24.580
What about you?

24:24.620 --> 24:26.070
You must be sad

24:26.090 --> 24:27.280
about your mother passing away too.

24:30.920 --> 24:32.160
Let me help you.

24:32.190 --> 24:33.750
In the future,

24:33.770 --> 24:34.970
don't keep things to yourself.

24:35.000 --> 24:36.590
Don't hurt yourself.

24:36.620 --> 24:38.230
I believe Uncle Bai and Shuo

24:38.270 --> 24:40.680
want to see you be truly happy.

24:46.760 --> 24:48.910
True happiness.

24:48.940 --> 24:50.120
Am I still qualified

24:50.720 --> 24:52.390
to have that in my life?

24:56.440 --> 24:57.370
You're awake.

24:59.800 --> 25:01.000
Drink the medicine while it's hot.

25:05.130 --> 25:06.570
Do you remember where this is?

25:08.680 --> 25:09.670
No.

25:09.730 --> 25:10.880
Why did you forcefully

25:10.880 --> 25:12.390
take me away from the Cold Spring Palace?

25:12.810 --> 25:15.100
No one willingly stays in hell.

25:15.190 --> 25:16.910
You had no choice before.

25:17.000 --> 25:18.030
Now,

25:18.060 --> 25:19.860
as long as you have enough courage

25:19.990 --> 25:22.050
to believe in yourself and me,

25:22.700 --> 25:24.170
you have a choice.

25:41.820 --> 25:42.610
I'm sorry.

25:43.550 --> 25:45.880
I told you I wouldn't let you get hurt.

25:47.440 --> 25:48.920
I failed to protect you.

25:49.810 --> 25:52.350
You can punish me as you want when you wake up.

25:54.150 --> 25:56.070
Wake up, Bai Shuo.

25:58.400 --> 25:59.280
Master.

25:59.530 --> 26:01.200
I failed to protect Bai Shuo.

26:16.320 --> 26:17.580
She managed to

26:17.600 --> 26:19.810
refine the contemplation power and spiritual power so quickly.

26:24.290 --> 26:25.270
Tian Huo?

26:27.090 --> 26:28.700
Why are you here?

26:31.130 --> 26:32.210
Where is Fan Yue?

26:32.270 --> 26:33.870
Master had something to deal with.

26:33.890 --> 26:35.020
He ordered me to be your guardian.

26:35.440 --> 26:37.440
He wouldn't leave me easily.

26:37.760 --> 26:39.300
Did something happen?

26:41.260 --> 26:43.100
The only one who can make Fan Yue worried

26:43.130 --> 26:44.610
is Chen Ye.

26:44.660 --> 26:46.480
Did he go to Cold Spring Palace?

26:48.180 --> 26:49.300
Tian Huo,

26:49.330 --> 26:50.440
tell me!

26:50.460 --> 26:51.660
Zhen Yu was the mastermind

26:51.690 --> 26:53.440
behind the Tiger Clan killing the Bai Ze Clan.

26:53.550 --> 26:55.220
Chen Ye went to take revenge on Zhen Yu

26:55.240 --> 26:56.630
and was caught by him.

26:58.370 --> 26:59.170
Bai Shuo!

27:00.230 --> 27:01.470
Move!

27:01.500 --> 27:03.090
I have no time to argue with you.

27:03.120 --> 27:04.800
Master must have his own plan.

27:12.000 --> 27:13.190
Bai Shuo.

27:13.380 --> 27:14.510
Tian Huo.

27:15.140 --> 27:16.900
You have your promise to uphold.

27:16.920 --> 27:19.090
I have a loved one to save.

27:19.120 --> 27:20.440
I must go.

27:21.080 --> 27:23.110
Bai Shuo! Bai Shuo!

27:23.560 --> 27:25.360
Open the barrier!

27:26.490 --> 27:28.540
I didn't fulfill your request.

27:28.610 --> 27:29.980
Please punish me.

27:31.120 --> 27:32.800
Her spiritual power is stronger than yours.

27:33.360 --> 27:34.450
You couldn't stop her.

27:35.080 --> 27:36.540
She trapped you in the cave

27:36.980 --> 27:38.380
because she didn't want me to punish you.

27:39.110 --> 27:40.460
Besides, I should be blamed,

27:40.480 --> 27:41.590
instead of you.

27:41.630 --> 27:43.960
If Bai Shuo hadn't given me the medicine in advance,

27:44.350 --> 27:45.950
you probably wouldn't have

27:46.090 --> 27:47.860
recovered so quickly from losing a star this time.

27:48.090 --> 27:48.940
Medicine?

27:49.700 --> 27:51.020
When did she give it to you?

27:51.050 --> 27:52.680
When you went to find the Old Turtle

27:52.700 --> 27:54.900
and asked why Bai Shuo had a nosebleed,

27:54.930 --> 27:56.440
you quarreled with her

27:56.470 --> 27:58.340
and broke her tortoise shell.

27:58.360 --> 27:59.830
Your life is yours.

27:59.870 --> 28:01.790
My life is mine.

28:01.820 --> 28:03.490
Why should they be bound?

28:03.740 --> 28:05.780
After that, she came to my room to look for me.

28:05.810 --> 28:07.460
This is the medicine I made these days

28:07.550 --> 28:09.090
after changing the formula.

28:09.120 --> 28:11.480
I don’t know if it’s useful on the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal.

28:11.640 --> 28:12.970
If he doesn’t appreciate it,

28:13.030 --> 28:15.350
give it to other wounded demons in Bright Moon Palace.

28:15.670 --> 28:16.520
Master...

28:18.510 --> 28:20.620
Master must have his reasons for saying that.

28:21.470 --> 28:23.230
He has his own reasons for everything.

28:23.260 --> 28:24.690
If he doesn't make it clear,

28:24.710 --> 28:26.760
how would I know what he meant?

28:26.790 --> 28:28.270
But you still cultivated the pill.

28:28.300 --> 28:29.910
You say you're unhappy,

28:29.930 --> 28:31.790
but you still care about him

28:31.810 --> 28:33.580
and the demons of Bright Moon Palace.

28:35.710 --> 28:36.960
She always says

28:36.960 --> 28:39.110
I risk my life to save her.

28:39.830 --> 28:40.920
But she also

28:40.920 --> 28:42.920
risks her life to save me.

28:44.040 --> 28:46.720
Her spiritual power is not as strong as yours,

28:46.740 --> 28:48.430
but she has four Contemplations of the Contemplation Stone

28:48.450 --> 28:50.280
and Bai Ze's spiritual power.

28:50.310 --> 28:52.180
Master, don’t worry too much.

28:53.810 --> 28:54.810
Master.

28:54.830 --> 28:55.980
You just recovered too.

28:56.010 --> 28:57.110
Go and rest.

28:57.130 --> 28:58.890
I'll call you when she wakes up.

29:17.890 --> 29:18.850
Tian Huo.

29:18.650 --> 29:20.550
[Qi Feng]

29:19.780 --> 29:21.940
Qi Feng never forgot who he was.

29:22.790 --> 29:24.200
Otherwise, he wouldn't have risked his life

29:24.200 --> 29:25.350
to take revenge on Zhen Yu.

29:26.130 --> 29:27.860
It’s hard to explain the love and hate,

29:28.030 --> 29:29.990
and right and wrong from these years.

29:30.850 --> 29:32.370
Let Cang Shan's hatred

29:33.380 --> 29:34.620
and Qi Feng's death

29:36.680 --> 29:38.240
scatter like the smoke.

29:40.310 --> 29:42.550
Master, you lost your good friends

29:42.580 --> 29:44.420
Cang Shan and Qi Feng one after another.

29:44.450 --> 29:46.410
You're the one in the most pain.

29:46.680 --> 29:48.920
I won't make things more difficult for you.

29:50.780 --> 29:52.240
Take care of Shuo here.

29:54.120 --> 29:57.390
[Qi Feng]

29:54.570 --> 29:56.050
I'll send Qi Feng

29:56.260 --> 29:57.600
back to the clan.

30:14.710 --> 30:15.780
This time,

30:15.830 --> 30:17.350
I invited you all here

30:17.380 --> 30:21.540
to ask all Sect Leaders to lead your disciples

30:22.110 --> 30:23.780
and join Lanling

30:23.810 --> 30:26.850
to unite the power of the 72 Eternal Sects

30:26.980 --> 30:30.070
and destroy Cold Spring Palace.

30:39.280 --> 30:40.490
Sect Leader Jin Yao,

30:40.510 --> 30:43.020
keeping peace is the obligation of the Eternals,

30:43.110 --> 30:45.280
but Zhen Yu's demonic power is unfathomable.

30:43.750 --> 30:47.150
[Xi Yun, Eternal Race, Yunxiao Sect Leader]

30:45.300 --> 30:46.250
Many disciples of ours

30:46.270 --> 30:48.180
have been killed by Cold Spring Palace these years.

30:49.070 --> 30:50.680
Lanling suddenly summoned all Eternal Sects

30:50.680 --> 30:52.180
to attack Cold Spring Palace.

30:52.210 --> 30:53.820
Isn't this too impulsive?

30:54.940 --> 30:56.260
I understand your worries.

30:56.280 --> 30:57.240
Correct.

30:57.040 --> 30:58.680
[Wu Ya, Eternal Race, Kunlun Sect Leader]

30:57.270 --> 31:00.070
If the 72 Sects attack Cold Spring Palace together,

31:00.100 --> 31:02.860
it'll be a declaration of war between the Eternal and Demon Races.

31:02.880 --> 31:04.320
This is a serious matter.

31:04.350 --> 31:06.680
I'm afraid the innocent Human Race will be implicated.

31:07.020 --> 31:07.910
Sect Leader,

31:07.930 --> 31:10.090
you have to give me a reason.

31:10.530 --> 31:12.120
-Yes.
-He's right.

31:12.150 --> 31:13.820
I found that

31:14.220 --> 31:17.030
Zhen Yu may be related to the Hidden Race.

31:17.930 --> 31:19.930
Hidden Race?

31:19.960 --> 31:21.160
Impossible.

31:21.180 --> 31:23.760
The Hidden Race was destroyed 60,000 years ago.

31:24.670 --> 31:25.880
Sect Leader Jin Yao,

31:25.900 --> 31:28.300
where did you get the information that Zhen Yu

31:28.330 --> 31:29.810
has something to do with the Hidden Race?

31:31.190 --> 31:33.360
Sect Leader Xi Yun, what do you mean?

31:33.380 --> 31:34.180
Are you

31:34.210 --> 31:35.040
suspecting

31:35.070 --> 31:36.990
that Lanling is lying?

31:37.010 --> 31:38.160
No,

31:38.190 --> 31:40.420
but this is a serious matter.

31:40.440 --> 31:42.480
If Zhen Yu really is related to the Hidden Race,

31:42.510 --> 31:43.990
we should be more careful

31:44.010 --> 31:45.140
about attacking him.

31:45.560 --> 31:47.280
If the Eternals

31:47.300 --> 31:48.620
always think too much,

31:49.070 --> 31:50.110
how can we cultivate

31:50.140 --> 31:51.410
or protect the world?

31:51.430 --> 31:51.840
You!

31:51.870 --> 31:53.150
I'm talking about him.

31:53.200 --> 31:56.110
This is not the time to argue.

31:57.070 --> 31:58.910
Before, we couldn't figure out

31:58.930 --> 32:01.000
the true strength of Cold Spring Palace,

32:01.130 --> 32:03.460
so we didn't dare to go to attack brashly.

32:04.220 --> 32:06.020
If we don’t take advantage of how

32:06.050 --> 32:09.010
Bright Moon Palace severely damaged Cold Spring Palace

32:09.030 --> 32:10.590
to take it down,

32:10.620 --> 32:13.620
I'm afraid there will be no chance in the future.

32:14.610 --> 32:18.220
Fan Yue is stronger than Zhen Yu,

32:18.250 --> 32:19.090
but

32:19.110 --> 32:22.310
the mechanisms and demonic abilities of Cold Spring Palace

32:22.340 --> 32:24.340
are not to be underestimated.

32:24.370 --> 32:26.680
Bright Moon Palace seriously hurting Cold Spring Palace

32:26.710 --> 32:28.490
is just hearsay.

32:28.650 --> 32:29.850
Did anyone here

32:29.870 --> 32:31.570
see it with their own eyes?

32:31.780 --> 32:32.990
Yeah.

32:33.600 --> 32:35.170
What if this is a conspiracy

32:35.240 --> 32:36.790
of Bright Moon Palace and Cold Spring Palace

32:36.810 --> 32:38.800
to lure us Eternals in

32:38.830 --> 32:39.940
and then

32:40.700 --> 32:43.060
catch us all in one go?

32:43.080 --> 32:44.970
That's right.

32:47.890 --> 32:49.820
Sect Leader Wu Ya is right.

32:49.850 --> 32:51.090
How can we act brashly

32:51.110 --> 32:52.530
just because of

32:52.550 --> 32:53.640
some rumors?

32:53.680 --> 32:55.730
Yes. What if it's a trap?

32:55.760 --> 32:57.430
This is indeed strange.

32:57.450 --> 32:58.970
We should not act rashly.

32:59.000 --> 32:59.810
That's right.

32:59.830 --> 33:00.860
We need a long-term plan.

33:00.880 --> 33:02.880
Sect Leader Jin Yao said

33:02.910 --> 33:05.350
the Cold Spring Palace was severely hurt by Bright Moon Palace.

33:06.270 --> 33:08.420
I have a question.

33:08.450 --> 33:09.570
Where is

33:09.770 --> 33:11.850
Zhen Yu now?

33:11.870 --> 33:14.390
Zhen Yu has escaped from the Cold Spring Palace

33:14.410 --> 33:15.820
and disappeared.

33:17.090 --> 33:18.570
That means

33:18.610 --> 33:20.530
he may return at any time.

33:20.550 --> 33:22.350
So everything is unknown.

33:22.820 --> 33:23.970
In my opinion,

33:24.000 --> 33:26.140
we should stay put

33:26.160 --> 33:28.420
before we find Zhen Yu.

33:28.490 --> 33:30.760
Yes, let's plan for the long-term.

33:31.290 --> 33:32.160
Yes.

33:32.180 --> 33:34.070
Stay put.

33:34.100 --> 33:35.610
Stay put.

33:47.720 --> 33:49.000
You're awake.

33:52.540 --> 33:53.540
Where is Fan Yue?

33:54.130 --> 33:55.540
You're just like Master.

33:55.570 --> 33:57.520
You look for each other as soon as you open your eyes.

33:58.290 --> 33:59.970
He must be badly injured too.

34:00.200 --> 34:01.360
He's still in a coma.

34:02.180 --> 34:03.610
Did he lose a star?

34:06.010 --> 34:07.240
I'll go check on him.

34:07.920 --> 34:10.090
He's fine after taking your medicine.

34:10.170 --> 34:11.080
But...

34:11.650 --> 34:12.960
Qi Feng is dead.

34:12.989 --> 34:14.320
He's sad.

34:14.460 --> 34:15.900
He's in the secret room now,

34:15.920 --> 34:18.290
reuniting Qi Feng with the other clansmen.

34:18.320 --> 34:19.469
Don't worry.

34:21.900 --> 34:22.940
By the way,

34:23.120 --> 34:25.020
I need to go to the Cold Spring Palace again.

34:25.050 --> 34:26.420
Xi might still be there.

34:27.480 --> 34:29.040
Bai Xi is not in the Cold Spring Palace.

34:29.070 --> 34:30.199
When you were still unconscious,

34:30.219 --> 34:31.429
I already went to search for her.

34:31.449 --> 34:32.840
But I saw her in Qi Feng's

34:32.840 --> 34:34.000
sea of consciousness.

34:34.020 --> 34:36.000
What you saw was from many years ago.

34:36.150 --> 34:37.500
After so many years,

34:37.530 --> 34:39.659
many unexpected things will happen.

34:39.960 --> 34:41.000
Besides,

34:41.030 --> 34:42.980
the Cold Spring Palace was severely damaged.

34:43.010 --> 34:44.639
The members escaped and scattered.

34:44.659 --> 34:46.340
If your sister was in Cold Spring Palace,

34:46.370 --> 34:47.960
she probably escaped.

34:50.130 --> 34:51.210
Don’t worry.

34:51.239 --> 34:53.030
I’ve sent spies from Bright Moon Palace

34:53.050 --> 34:54.739
to keep searching for her.

34:55.800 --> 34:57.510
Thank you, Tian Huo.

34:59.240 --> 35:01.280
We don't say thanks in Bright Moon Palace.

35:05.960 --> 35:06.670
Sect Leader,

35:06.670 --> 35:08.110
why didn’t you tell them

35:08.110 --> 35:10.630
we asked Chong Zhao to go undercover to Cold Spring?

35:10.650 --> 35:12.360
Chong Zhao risked his life

35:12.400 --> 35:13.680
to get this information.

35:13.730 --> 35:15.330
As you can see,

35:15.360 --> 35:16.840
they don’t even believe me anymore.

35:16.860 --> 35:18.090
How could they believe

35:18.120 --> 35:19.470
the message Chong Zhao sent back?

35:19.500 --> 35:22.240
The Eternals are in chaos now.

35:22.260 --> 35:23.610
Once they find out

35:23.640 --> 35:25.870
Chong Zhao used to work for Zhen Yu,

35:26.010 --> 35:29.010
he won't be accepted by the Eternals

35:29.030 --> 35:31.390
when he returns to the Eternal Race.

35:31.420 --> 35:32.750
Besides...

35:33.740 --> 35:34.620
Sect Leader,

35:34.640 --> 35:35.900
please go ahead.

35:36.250 --> 35:38.210
In Chong Zhao’s letter,

35:38.240 --> 35:40.320
he said he was forced to practice

35:40.340 --> 35:42.610
the magic of combining the power of eternals and demons.

35:42.640 --> 35:45.210
This kind of sorcery can only be integrated

35:45.230 --> 35:46.760
with hidden power.

35:46.790 --> 35:49.060
Sect Leader, you mean Chong Zhao

35:49.080 --> 35:51.380
not only has demon power, but also hidden power?

35:51.850 --> 35:55.000
The Hidden Race and hidden power are not tolerated by eternals and demons.

35:55.030 --> 35:58.240
If other sects know that Chong Zhao has hidden power,

35:58.360 --> 36:01.010
he might lose his life.

36:03.120 --> 36:04.850
This child risked his life

36:04.870 --> 36:07.990
and experienced humiliation for Lanling.

36:08.130 --> 36:09.830
As his teachers and seniors,

36:09.860 --> 36:12.560
how can we push him into a desperate situation again?

36:12.580 --> 36:14.820
This reptile is just one word:

36:14.850 --> 36:16.140
vicious!

36:16.390 --> 36:19.590
I will seek justice for Chong Zhao.

36:19.620 --> 36:20.490
But now,

36:20.510 --> 36:22.430
I have to go find Chong Zhao

36:22.460 --> 36:24.390
and see how he is now.

36:24.410 --> 36:25.300
Sect Leader,

36:25.330 --> 36:27.040
we watched Chong Zhao grow up.

36:27.060 --> 36:28.300
We're going too!

36:28.690 --> 36:31.360
No, the situation is still unclear.

36:31.430 --> 36:33.200
You all guard Lanling.

36:33.220 --> 36:35.220
I will protect Chong Zhao.

36:35.250 --> 36:36.210
Remember,

36:36.230 --> 36:38.350
you must guard Lanling.

36:41.440 --> 36:43.610
We won't let you down.

36:52.460 --> 36:55.020
[Qi Feng]

37:02.260 --> 37:04.260
[Qi Feng]

37:13.320 --> 37:19.580
[Yue, I'm sorry.]

37:19.260 --> 37:22.650
♫Don't linger, don't regret♫

37:23.680 --> 37:26.040
♫The last moonlight♫

37:27.320 --> 37:30.760
♫The water from my hometown flows gently♫

37:32.150 --> 37:34.690
♫Sending me to the distant place♫

37:32.880 --> 37:34.430
Yue.

37:35.490 --> 37:39.460
♫In this life, at this time♫

37:35.990 --> 37:37.240
I'm sorry.

37:39.830 --> 37:43.000
♫I dare not look back♫

37:41.360 --> 37:43.240
If none of this had happened,

37:43.780 --> 37:47.150
♫Is there the same moonlight♫

37:44.210 --> 37:46.480
would we still be best friends?

37:48.330 --> 37:51.230
♫On your path?♫

37:52.240 --> 37:55.180
♫I'm walking on a never-ending long road♫

37:55.630 --> 37:59.060
♫In the vast world, how can I get there?♫

37:59.750 --> 38:01.610
♫In the chaotic night wind, the melody stopped♫

38:02.260 --> 38:04.090
♫The moonlight is gentle♫

38:04.610 --> 38:07.620
♫All the feelings turned into nothing but a dream♫

38:08.410 --> 38:11.460
♫Reminiscing about the good old days♫

38:11.800 --> 38:15.230
♫Singing until the voice fades, I'm feeling lost♫

38:15.580 --> 38:17.900
♫Forget all about the past and leave it behind♫

38:18.630 --> 38:19.960
♫Time after time♫

38:21.200 --> 38:25.580
♫Oh, melancholy♫

38:52.250 --> 38:53.690
Tian Huo told me

38:54.190 --> 38:56.410
you come here when you're unhappy.

38:59.580 --> 39:00.950
Cang Shan is gone.

39:00.970 --> 39:02.370
Qi Feng is gone too.

39:02.400 --> 39:03.590
You suddenly have the new identity

39:03.590 --> 39:05.220
of a Demon Lord's Divine Mantle now.

39:05.250 --> 39:06.910
So many things have happened.

39:06.930 --> 39:08.210
If I were you,

39:08.360 --> 39:09.850
I'd feel troubled too.

39:10.300 --> 39:12.410
I know you're used to being stubborn.

39:13.030 --> 39:14.560
But in front of me,

39:14.580 --> 39:16.260
you don't have to hide yourself.

39:17.080 --> 39:18.230
You said

39:18.250 --> 39:19.600
we are family.

39:25.500 --> 39:27.930
When I built the palace and called myself the king of the Polar Region,

39:28.630 --> 39:30.020
I swore

39:31.000 --> 39:32.740
to protect everyone around me

39:33.240 --> 39:35.830
and prevent the pain of Bai Ze from happening again.

39:36.320 --> 39:38.270
But in the end, I let Cang Shan and Qi Feng

39:38.300 --> 39:39.450
leave me.

39:40.700 --> 39:42.660
And you were hurt too.

39:43.580 --> 39:44.620
Fan Yue,

39:45.400 --> 39:47.420
you are also of flesh and blood.

39:48.610 --> 39:50.690
You also bleed, get hurt,

39:50.710 --> 39:52.440
and get sad.

39:53.190 --> 39:54.440
You are no different from

39:54.440 --> 39:56.070
the people you want to protect.

39:57.110 --> 39:58.630
Your strength is not

39:58.670 --> 40:00.550
the reason to blame yourself.

40:08.050 --> 40:09.820
You're the best at consoling me.

40:11.320 --> 40:12.690
Thank you, Shuo.

40:16.330 --> 40:17.830
It's not just consolation,

40:18.070 --> 40:19.340
but also a reminder.

40:19.370 --> 40:21.330
You only have one star left.

40:21.500 --> 40:23.390
Don't act tough when you're in trouble.

40:23.480 --> 40:24.490
Understand?

40:24.760 --> 40:25.720
For you,

40:26.490 --> 40:28.210
I'll continue to live well.

40:31.930 --> 40:32.850
I promise you.

40:38.270 --> 40:41.900
♫The person standing far away♫

40:42.680 --> 40:44.840
♫Don't be afraid♫

40:45.410 --> 40:49.690
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

40:49.220 --> 40:51.500
Turns out the Demon Race has fireflies too.

40:50.870 --> 40:57.170
♫Walk towards me♫

40:51.530 --> 40:53.130
Autumn breeze blows grass

40:53.160 --> 40:54.550
and fireflies fly at night.

40:54.920 --> 40:57.290
This should be the last batch of fireflies this year.

40:58.990 --> 41:01.970
♫My heart feels so...♫

41:02.400 --> 41:08.000
♫It's pounding as I wait for you♫

41:06.410 --> 41:07.490
Shuo.

41:08.730 --> 41:11.350
Actually, I think you resemble this firefly.

41:09.950 --> 41:14.250
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

41:12.310 --> 41:13.790
The dim glow in the night

41:15.190 --> 41:17.580
is the hope that dispels the darkness and clouds.

41:17.850 --> 41:21.000
♫You are my distant call♫

41:18.180 --> 41:19.660
You mean

41:19.680 --> 41:21.410
I'm your hope

41:21.510 --> 41:22.620
and your light?

41:21.610 --> 41:26.120
♫You are my first and last♫

41:26.710 --> 41:32.740
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

41:28.820 --> 41:30.150
You've always been.

41:31.760 --> 41:33.640
I heard that the Divine Race is immortal.

41:33.060 --> 41:36.020
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

41:33.660 --> 41:35.870
Maybe you will be young forever.

41:36.350 --> 41:37.950
Since I'm so important,

41:36.600 --> 41:40.480
♫Let's never let go♫

41:37.970 --> 41:39.800
when I get old,

41:39.880 --> 41:41.900
you have to stay with me

41:42.370 --> 41:43.550
and take care of me.

41:44.170 --> 41:45.890
Don't die first.

41:46.310 --> 41:47.240
Okay.

41:48.520 --> 41:49.900
In this life

41:50.430 --> 41:51.740
and every life,

41:52.420 --> 41:54.190
I will never leave you.

41:54.940 --> 41:56.340
Your words

41:56.810 --> 41:58.600
sound like an oath.

41:58.770 --> 41:59.920
It is an oath.

42:00.630 --> 42:04.810
♫We're destined to be together forever from the first sight♫

42:05.250 --> 42:07.400
♫Goodbye, loneliness♫

42:08.340 --> 42:11.460
♫The one who was slightly late♫

42:12.810 --> 42:19.830
♫You came towards me, closer and closer♫

42:13.720 --> 42:15.600
Then let me give you one too, okay?

42:16.170 --> 42:17.650
May I be like the stars

42:17.670 --> 42:19.010
and you like the moon.

42:19.660 --> 42:21.100
As long as the world remains,

42:21.230 --> 42:28.070
♫You enriched my life♫

42:21.740 --> 42:22.890
the stars and moon remain,

42:23.940 --> 42:25.020
so shall we.

42:31.740 --> 42:36.810
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

42:39.640 --> 42:43.150
♫You are the light I yearn for♫

42:43.810 --> 42:48.330
♫You are my determined way home♫

42:48.660 --> 42:54.320
♫Let this moment stay forever♫

42:54.830 --> 42:58.560
♫I'm hugging you in the crowd♫

42:59.100 --> 43:01.580
♫Let's never let go♫

43:01.990 --> 43:06.980
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

43:09.270 --> 43:13.210
♫You are the blueprint of my life♫

43:13.840 --> 43:18.130
♫The morning breeze and morning dew♫

43:18.610 --> 43:22.890
♫Let the tears celebrate♫

43:24.810 --> 43:28.300
♫We embrace each other in the sky♫

43:28.780 --> 43:32.180
♫Let's never let go♫
